Placeholder for PCHelper application icon.

Create a 256x256 PNG icon with:
- Dark background (#0d1117)
- A stylized "P" letter centered, using accent color (#58a6ff)
- Subtle circuit-board or chip pattern behind the letter
- Rounded corners (suggested)

This file is required by electron-builder for the Windows installer.
Replace this note with the actual icon.png before building.

To generate a quick placeholder:
- Use any PNG generator, or
- Create a simple SVG and convert: npx svg-to-png assets/icon.svg assets/icon.png
